data.description: SELLER contributing up to $8,500.00 to use however you want!!!! Unmissable Opportunity!! One story home for sale at a competitive price!! Bring your VISION and TLC - Motivated Seller Awaits!!! You will fall in love with this 3 Bedrooms 2 Full Bath home in the highly desired Cross Creek neighborhood. Perfect for entertaining with an open layout, large kitchen with beautiful island that will delight any aspiring chef. Oversized master bedroom a must see.... and a spacious master bath with a nice standup shower. Close to Sea World, military base, hospitals, and Northside ISD schools. Home also features, Reverse Osmosis water filter, water softener, sprinkler system back and front, and gutters. A MUST SEE!
